---
// src/pages/egitimler.astro
---

<html lang="tr">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>İnteraktif Eğitimler - BIPlaybook</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
</head>
<body>

    <!-- ÜST PANEL (NAVBAR) -->
    <nav class="navbar">
        <div class="nav-container">
            <a href="/" class="logo">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-chart-line logo-icon"></i>
                <span class="logo-text">BI<span class="logo-text-bold">Playbook</span></span>
            </a>
            
            <ul class="nav-links">
                <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
                <li><a href="/blog">Blog</a></li>
                <li><a href="/egitimler" class="active">Eğitimler</a></li>
                <li><a href="/about">About</a></li>
            </ul>

            <div class="social-icons">
                <a href="#"><i class="fa-brands fa-github"></i></a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <!-- EĞİTİM MERKEZİ BAŞLIĞI -->
    <header class="page-header">
        <div class="container">
            <h1>İnteraktif Eğitim Merkezi</h1>
            <p>Pratik yaparak öğrenin. Hangi yeteneğinizi geliştirmek istersiniz?</p>
        </div>
    </header>

    <!-- KURS MODÜLLERİ -->
    <section class="courses-section">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="courses-grid">
                
                <!-- SQL Kursu -->
                <div class="course-card">
                    <div class="course-icon sql-theme">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-database"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="course-content">
                        <h3>İnteraktif SQL Eğitimi</h3>
                        <p>Tarayıcı üzerinden gerçek veri setleriyle kod yazarak SQL öğrenin. Sorguları çalıştırın, sonuçları anında görün.</p>
                        <div class="course-meta">
                            <span><i class="fa-solid fa-layer-group"></i> 12 Modül</span>
                            <span><i class="fa-solid fa-signal"></i> Başlangıç - İleri</span>
                        </div>
                        <a href="/sql-ogren" class="btn btn-start sql-btn">Eğitime Başla <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right"></i></a>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- SAP Kursu -->
                <div class="course-card">
                    <div class="course-icon sap-theme">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-cube"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="course-content">
                        <h3>SAP Modül Pratikleri</h3>
                        <p>SD, MM ve FI modüllerindeki temel veri akışlarını simüle edin ve tablolar arası ilişkileri kavrayın.</p>
                        <div class="course-meta">
                            <span><i class="fa-solid fa-layer-group"></i> 8 Modül</span>
                            <span><i class="fa-solid fa-signal"></i> Orta Seviye</span>
                        </div>
                        <a href="/sap-ogren" class="btn btn-start sap-btn">Simülasyonlara Git <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right"></i></a>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- İş Zekası / BI Kursu (YAKINDA) -->
                <div class="course-card disabled-card">
                    <div class="course-icon bi-theme">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-chart-pie"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="course-content">
                        <h3>Dinamik Dashboard Tasarımı</h3>
                        <p>Qlik Sense ve PowerBI mantığıyla veri modelleme ve görselleştirme senaryoları üzerinde çalışın.</p>
                        <div class="course-meta">
                            <span><i class="fa-solid fa-layer-group"></i> 5 Proje</span>
                            <span><i class="fa-solid fa-signal"></i> Orta Seviye</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="btn btn-start btn-disabled"><i class="fa-solid fa-clock"></i> Çok Yakında</div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- ETL Kursu (YAKINDA) -->
                <div class="course-card disabled-card">
                    <div class="course-icon etl-theme">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-network-wired"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="course-content">
                        <h3>ETL Veri Boru Hatları</h3>
                        <p>Farklı kaynaklardan veriyi çekip, temizleyip, dönüştürerek hedef sisteme aktarma (Data Pipeline) egzersizleri.</p>
                        <div class="course-meta">
                            <span><i class="fa-solid fa-layer-group"></i> 6 Senaryo</span>
                            <span><i class="fa-solid fa-signal"></i> İleri Seviye</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="btn btn-start btn-disabled"><i class="fa-solid fa-clock"></i> Çok Yakında</div>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

</body>
</html>

<style>
    :root {
        --nav-bg: #0d1117; 
        --bg-dark: #0a0e17; 
        --bg-darker: #02060f;
        --text-main: #f0f6fc;
        --text-muted: #8b949e;
        --border-color: #30363d;
        
        --sql-color: #f59e0b;
        --sap-color: #3b82f6;
        --bi-color: #10b981;
        --etl-color: #a855f7;
    }

    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

    body {
        font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
        background-color: var(--bg-dark);
        color: var(--text-main);
        line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .container {
        max-width: 1100px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 0 20px;
    }

    /* NAVBAR */
    .navbar {
        background-color: var(--nav-bg);
        border-bottom: 1px solid #1f2937;
        position: sticky;
        top: 0;
        z-index: 1000;
    }

    .nav-container {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: space-between;
        height: 70px;
        max-width: 1200px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 0 20px;
    }

    .logo {
        color: white;
        text-decoration: none;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 8px;
    }

    .logo-icon { font-size: 1.4rem; color: var(--sql-color); }
    .logo-text { font-size: 1.25rem; }
    .logo-text-bold { font-weight: 700; }

    .nav-links { display: flex; list-style: none; height: 100%; gap: 1.5rem; }
    .nav-links li { height: 100%; display: flex; align-items: center; }
    .nav-links a {
        color: #e5e7eb; text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 500;
        height: 100%; display: flex; align-items: center; border-bottom: 3px solid transparent; transition: color 0.2s;
    }
    .nav-links a:hover { color: white; }
    .nav-links a.active { color: white; font-weight: 600; border-bottom: 3px solid var(--sql-color); }

    .social-icons a { color: #9ca3af; font-size: 1.1rem; transition: color 0.2s; }
    .social-icons a:hover { color: white; }

    /* HEADER */
    .page-header {
        padding: 60px 0 40px;
        text-align: center;
        background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(2,6,15,1) 0%, var(--bg-dark) 100%);
    }

    .page-header h1 {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .page-header p {
        color: var(--text-muted);
        font-size: 1.1rem;
    }

    /* KURS KARTLARI */
    .courses-section {
        padding: 40px 0 80px;
    }

    .courses-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(400px, 1fr));
        gap: 2rem;
    }

    .course-card {
        background-color: #0d1117;
        border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
        border-radius: 12px;
        display: flex;
        padding: 1.5rem;
        gap: 1.5rem;
        transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s, border-color 0.2s;
    }

    .course-card:not(.disabled-card):hover {
        transform: translateY(-4px);
        border-color: #4b5563;
        box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
    }

    /* YAKINDA OLAN KARTLAR İÇİN HAFİF SOLUKLUK */
    .disabled-card {
        opacity: 0.85;
    }

    .course-icon {
        width: 70px;
        height: 70px;
        border-radius: 10px;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        font-size: 2rem;
        flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .sql-theme { background-color: rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.1); color: var(--sql-color); }
    .sap-theme { background-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.1); color: var(--sap-color); }
    .bi-theme  { background-color: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.1); color: var(--bi-color); }
    .etl-theme { background-color: rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.1); color: var(--etl-color); }

    .disabled-card .bi-theme { background-color: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.05); color: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.5); }
    .disabled-card .etl-theme { background-color: rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.05); color: rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.5); }

    .course-content {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        flex: 1;
    }

    .course-content h3 {
        font-size: 1.3rem;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .course-content p {
        color: var(--text-muted);
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        line-height: 1.5;
    }

    .course-meta {
        display: flex;
        gap: 1rem;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    .course-meta span {
        font-size: 0.8rem;
        color: #9ca3af;
        background-color: #1f2937;
        padding: 4px 10px;
        border-radius: 20px;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 6px;
    }

    .btn-start {
        margin-top: auto;
        padding: 10px 0;
        text-align: center;
        border-radius: 6px;
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        text-decoration: none;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        gap: 8px;
        transition: background-color 0.2s, color 0.2s;
    }

    .sql-btn { background-color: rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.15); color: var(--sql-color); }
    .sql-btn:hover { background-color: var(--sql-color); color: #000; }

    .sap-btn { background-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.15); color: var(--sap-color); }
    .sap-btn:hover { background-color: var(--sap-color); color: #fff; }

    /* YAKINDA BUTONU TASARIMI */
    .btn-disabled { 
        background-color: #161b22; 
        color: #6b7280; 
        border: 1px dashed #30363d;
        cursor: not-allowed;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .courses-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
        .course-card { flex-direction: column; }
        .course-icon { width: 60px; height: 60px; font-size: 1.5rem; }
    }
</style>